  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0d91\u0db1 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dad\u0dca \u0d85\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The number of people coming to hospitals also decreases",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the ongoing fuel crisis and the problems of getting transportation facilities, there is a lack of staff attendance at hospitals as well as patients coming to receive treatment from hospitals, according to health departments.",
        "According to hospital sources, the arrival of patients to hospitals has decreased by about 40 percent.",
        "The sources say that there is a decrease in the number of patients coming to receive treatment from the outpatient department and clinics of many hospitals such as Colombo National Hospital, Maharagama Cancer Hospital, Maligawatta Kidney Hospital, Lady Ridgeway Children's Hospital etc.",
        "Mr. Ravi Kumudesh, President of the Scholarly Association of Health Professionals, said that there has been a decrease in the number of patients visiting the hospitals as well as conducting laboratory tests.",
        "He said that the arrival of patients may have decreased due to the lack of transport facilities to visit the hospitals, the shortage of medicines in the hospitals or the lack of consideration of the health problems of the people.",
        "He said that although the program of providing fuel to the health workers is about 50 percent successful, the health services will also collapse on Friday as they have to wait in queues throughout the day.",
        "Mr. Ravi Kumudesh mentioned that at a time when the people are facing difficulties due to the shortage of medicines in the hospitals, it is not possible to carry out certain laboratory tests.",
        "Mr. Kumudesh also said that this problem has arisen due to the shortage of laboratory materials due to the non-payment of loans of about 10 billion rupees to be paid to the suppliers of laboratory materials.",
        "Also, many patients receiving treatment for cancer and undergoing blood transfusions due to kidney disease have been seen posting requests on social media asking if there is anyone who can provide them with facilities to go to hospitals."
      ],
